snippet.description:
#music #track #new #hype #jesvi

Hey Y'all,

Jesvi here with a new track for this month.
It was the intro chords that popped up first and then came the drop idea,  spent some time with overall production, and voila ! the result : 
The music in this track resembles more like my own style/genre from 'warrior' that was released 2 years ago...

I hope the time spent on these stuff is worth it in the end... 

The vocals used in this track are un edited, meaning they are not processed and are put in the way it was given by the singer..
The album art is one of Julian Frener's work on instagram; check out his work, they are amazing.


Track Details -

Title - Other Side
Genre - Future House, Bounce, EDM
Vocals - Michael Mayo (https://www.itsmichaelmayo.com/
Album Art - Julian Frener (https://instagram.com/frenerdesign?utm_medium=copy_link
Music, Video & Production - Jesvi Jonathan
